      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先搭建整体框架。最外层用LR横向布局，然后创建三个subgraph：Source、AXIS、Sink。AXIS内部再嵌套Signals和Protocol两个子图。",
